No.-. Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Gordon R. McGee, Petitioner. Submitted March 3, 1913. Decided March 10, 1913. Mr. Frans E. Lindquist for the petitioner. Per Curiam.

-The motion for

leave to file petition, for writ of habeas corpus is denied. (Ex parte Webb, 225 U. S. 663, 674, and authorities there cited.)
